data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of Stockbridge, GA! Presenting 137 Hambrick Dr, where luxury meets comfort in this stunning family retreat. Located in a prime neighborhood, this immaculate property offers an unparalleled living experience.  Spacious Layout: Sprawled across 5300 sqft +- this residence boasts ample space for every family member to enjoy. With 6 bedrooms and 6 bathrooms, there's room for everyone to thrive. Step into a world of modern convenience with a gourmet kitchen featuring sleek appliances, granite countertops, and ample storage space. The open-concept design flows seamlessly into the living area, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying cozy family nights.Retreat to the master suite for ultimate relaxation. Complete with a spa-like ensuite bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet, this sanctuary is designed for comfort and tranquility. Tranquil Outdoor Oasis: Escape to your own private paradise in the backyard oasis. Whether you're hosting BBQs on the patio, unwinding in the lush garden, or basking in the sun by the pool, this outdoor space is sure to impress.  Situated in a coveted neighborhood of Stockbridge, this home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Enjoy easy access to top-rated schools, shopping centers, dining options, and recreational activities.
